		H.set_blindness(0)
		var/trades = list("Town Physician","Farmer","Tailor","Laborer","Merchant","Levy") //JMAN COMBAT SKILLS... AND TOWNER TRADES. GOD I HOPE THIS ISN'T A TERRIBLE IDEA.
